    "These frames, along with the frame elements used for identifying relevant tables, can be found in Table 6 in the Appendix.",
    "PolitiFact fact-checks.",
    "For our analysis, we utilized a dataset of 21,024 PolitiFact fact-check articles (i.e., fact-checks) collected as of April 2022.",
